Package ohos.sysappcomponents.contact.entity

Class Contact

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.sysappcomponents.contact.entity.Contact

  • public class Contact
extends Object
    Provides information about a contact.

    This class provides methods to obtain basic attributes of a contact, such as the email address, event information, group information, instant messaging (IM) address, name, nickname, note, organization, phone number, portrait, postal address, relation, SIP address, and website.

    Since:
    4
